Program: Outlook
Title: Jose Poblete and Argentina's Dirty War
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03kbshq
Last Broadcast Date: Not available
Investigating the case of Jose Poblete and his wife, two of the disappeared during The Dirty War in Argentina, with comment from Andrew Graham-Yooll. Also, the woman who paid 15 million US dollars for 8 years ballroom dancing tuition in Hong Kong. Listeners' memorable journeys. Brian Copeland on living as a black man in an exclusive white US suburb. Finally, shoes made from fish skins in Uganda. Show less